1,"uid":78440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T15:05:42.000Z","msg":"「疾風知勁草，本人將會堅定不移，為香港人福祉，作出明智的決定，即使社會上有反對聲音。」<br />\n<br />\n最後，通過。<br />\n<br />\n然後到第23條。"},{"pid":"085f02a88e5dad8268becaff2e12baca4cf64672","tid":1195021,"uid":179731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e9372dafdd5d1acdb72183cc8c4b37f7c56a744","tid":1195021,"uid":4672,"like":172,"dislike":1,"score":171,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T13:39:14.000Z","msg":"「理解市民唔清楚條例細節而攞我出氣」<br />\n「特首係可以比市民出氣」<br />\n「會繼續遊說各界」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T15:06:22.000Z","msg":"見字都燥燥地"},{"pid":"601fe6279a375e48a60002a0d5596c109ea1eb7a","tid":1195021,"uid":64009,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T15:09:20.000Z","msg":"為左正義<br />\n條例一定要過"},{"pid":"15f9d30115d6ad29367230eb099cc5a243179952","tid":1195021,"uid":213171,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"5f098229d3852b15498d365fcd62dea9c0846219","tid":1195021,"uid":213171,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T14:30:58.000Z","msg":"777：政府會聆聽15.3萬人意見。送中條例會於6月12日準時二讀。多謝大家。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T15:25:02.000Z","msg":"政府：遊行人數雖然很多　條例將如期周三恢復二讀辯論<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1461758-20190609.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1461758-20190609.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=sUHHPMw%2FtTWAhlV0Ap%2Bq47HKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=5e65ec2c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1461758-20190609.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=94055767\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1461758-20190609.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n我估中了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0090e2339e12963397264312ce8666ea8cf353d","tid":1195021,"uid":164050,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":